Package shaharas

Class PatternsUtils

java.lang.Object
shaharas.PatternsUtils
final class PatternsUtils extends Object
Utility class that holds the regular expression patterns for various types of operators, assignment operations, variable and number patterns, and parentheses. This class is designed to avoid instantiation and only provides static constants for use in the program.
